snippet: Rory McIlroy found himself nine shots off the lead after a one-over-par 73 in the first round of the Alfred Dunhill Links Championship in Scotland.
abstract: Oliver Wilson holds lead following first round of the Alfred Dunhill Links Championship as Rory McIlroy finds himself nine strokes behind; other golf news noted.
